Restoring from backups
======================

This chapter discusses how to restore data from any backup generation,
either everything or individual files. It describes both the approach
using using the FUSE filesystem plugin, or using the `obnam restore`
command.

Oh no! It's all FUSEd together
------------------------------

This section describes how to use the FUSE plugin in Obnam to mount
the backup repository and restore by using file copying with various
tools, including rsync.

Restoring without FUSE
----------------------

This section describes how to restore data using the `obnam restore`
command.
